|MKOThroughout the centuries, thief brethren have developed "alternative" 
means of communication to avoid having their plots discovered by the likes
of the common God-fearing citizen. Many variations of thieves cant have 
spread through the alleyways and dark corners of the realms - the known cant
among Darkwind brethren is one spoken entirely by hand. This command is 
most effective when used in conjunction with hide, as the common citizen 
will not be able to see your subtle hand signals.

|CKOCommon uses include:
|MKB-|MKOSilent communication while hiding in the shadows setting up for a hit.
|MKB-|MKOMaking fun of a non-thief.

